Name: GORE-TEX Ocean Racer
Description: The GORE-TEX Ocean Racer Boot: made for the harshest conditions. For complete waterproof protection and optimal breathability, the boot features the toughest GORE-TEX footwear membrane available. The CORDURA® upper and gaiter ensures outstanding durability. Areas prone to abrasion damage have also been reinforced with scratch rubber for complete protection. GripDeck rubber and a GripFlex tread to supplies exceptional, multi-directional traction on deck. And a unique DynamicFit bellowed tongue and bungee lacing system provides a locked-down, comfort fit.

Name: Women's Classic Snug Blouson Jacket
Description: Launched in 1988, the Snug Blouson became a firm favourite among sailors and riders alike. This showerproof Women's Snug Blouson is lined with super-warm, 240g fleece for additional insulation. The high collar, inspired by Musto sailing jackets, supplies enhanced weather protection. A ribbed hem and cuffs ensure a snug fit.

Name: Women's MPX GORE-TEX Pro Offshore Trousers
Description: Sailing offshore requires full protection. These Women's MPX GORE-TEX Trousers feature a 3-layer GORE-TEX Pro fabric construction for superior waterproof, windproof and breathable protection. Reinforced CORDURA® knee, seat and back hem patches greatly enhance durability in key areas. For a tailored, comfort fit, use the adjustable shoulder straps, back waist and ankles, and elasticated under arms.

Name: Women's BR2 Offshore Jacket
Description: Constructed from supremely breathable, waterproof and windproof proprietary BR2 fabric. This Women's BR2 Offshore Jacket features super-engineered double cuffs, adjustable hem, double storm flap with a drainage channel over the zip and roll-away fluorescent hood for a superior level of dryness. A technical fleece-lined collar and handwarmer pockets enhance warmth while advanced prismatic reflectors provide visibility for safety in low light.

Name: Women's Musto Favourite T-Shirt
Description: This 100% cotton Women's Favourite T-Shirt offers breathable comfort. A minimalist design ensures versatility, allowing it to be worn alone or layered under a shirt or knitwear.

Name: Women's BR1 Trousers
Description: Get the foul weather protection you need for inshore and coastal sailing with the Women's BR1 Trousers. Waterproof, breathable and windproof you will stay dry and comfortable whatever the weather. Reinforced knees, seat and back hems add durability in high-wear areas. Elasticated shoulder straps, underarms and back waist give you the ideal snug fit so you can sail in comfort. Also, the detachable multi-tool pouch provides somewhere to keep tools and the thigh pocket, with a water-deflecting closure, will keep essentials close to hand. Everything you need for your sail.

Name: WOMEN'S EVOLUTION OSM TECHNICAL HOODIE
Description: Much more than your average hoodie – the Evolution OSM Tech Hoodie is both sustainable and stylish. Made from one single material, the garment will be much easier to recycle at the end of its life.

Name: Women's BR2 Offshore Trouser
Description: Designed for the needs of the serious female offshore sailor, these trousers have been engineered in a new feminine fit for tailored comfort and protection in foul weather at sea. Breathable and durably waterproof, this garment provides extensive protection, with the articulated seat and knee constructions to ensure freedom of movement even under layers. For added wear-resistance, these hi-fit trousers feature seat and knee patches, while water-resistant pockets ensure your personal items stay safe and dry.

Name: WOMEN'S EVOLUTION NEWPORT OSM PRIMALOFT® PARKA
Description: Designed in collaboration with 11th Hour Racing, our Evolution Newport OSM PRIMALOFT® Parka delivers style and substance for conscientious adventurers who care about protecting the environment as much as they do themselves. The jacket is constructed from One Single Material (OSM) which makes it much easier to recycle at the end of its life. This is especially important for the environment as recycling fibres helps to reduce the overuse of raw virgin materials. Complete with Musto’s BR2 performance technology and PRIMALOFT® Silver Eco insulation – 100% recycled polyester - this jacket still delivers on our commitment to utilising premium fabric technologies without compromising on sustainability or style.

The seams down the arms give maximum freedom of movement and avoid high-stress points so it lasts for longer.

Name: Clipper Race Fast Dry Cap
Description: Most ocean races are unpredictable. The Clipper Race is no different. One thing you can be sure of: you will get wet! Enter the Clipper Fast Dry Cap. The fabric dries rapidly and protects you from the sun with its added UV protection properties. The peak will shield your eyes from the sun and the rear adjustment gives you a secure fit. Don’t lose it in high winds - attach the retainer clip!

Name: Women's Whisper Highland GORE-TEX® Primaloft® Jacket
Description: The Whisper GORE-TEX® PrimaLoft® Jacket features supremely smooth brushed fabric with a tricot face. A GORE Woodland Liner provides windproof, waterproof and breathable protection while a Durable Water Repellent coating adds further weather-resistance. PrimaLoft® Silver insulation delivers incredible warmth while the waist adjuster can be used via the handwarmer pockets.

Name: Frome Mid Layer Salopette
Description: Fleece lined for superior warmth and insulation, these Frome Mid Layer Salopettes offer impeccable insulation out on the water. Elastication along the back of the waist delivers prolonged comfort and freedom of movement on the boat. Featuring an updated aesthetic with signature Musto red trims. Designed for freezing conditions when adding a layer of warmth is paramount. Worn by Volvo Ocean Race sailors as part of Musto's 3-layer system.

Name: Women's Sixty Four Knit
Description: To commemorate the year that Musto founder Keith Musto sailed to Olympic Silver medal victory in Tokyo, the Women's Sixty Four Knit is made with 100% Pima Cotton and features a scooped neck and contrast tipping around the collar.

Name: Women's Evolution Performance Trouser 2.0
Description: These are hard-wearing women's sailing trousers developed in a lightweight, fast dry stretch fabric for full freedom of movement and comfort. Schoeller®-keprotec® reinforcement on the seat, knees and back hem give these trousers durability. Back and thigh pockets keep your possessions close and secure.

Name: Youth Championship Drysuit
Description: This Youth Championship Drysuit features an exceptionally waterproof and breathable construction with advanced latex seals and socks. The Dynat® zip, mounted on a neoprenic tape, creates a watertight seal to ensure a superior level of dryness. Reinforced seat and knees reduce wear, with articulated sleeves for complete freedom of movement.

Name: Sunblock Dynamic Pant
Description: Featuring an Ultraviolet Protection Factor (UPF) of 50, the Sunblock Dynamic Pant will keep you protected from strong sun exposure. The fabrication is infused with Xylitol, an active cooling agent that will help you stay comfortable in even the most humid conditions, and the garment also features Kevlar® which prevents wear and protects the fabric from abrasion on the seat and knees.

Name: Musto 90L Duffel Bag
Description: Whether you're off on a long voyage or embarking on a big adventure, the Musto 90L Duffel Bag is lightweight, durable and provides you with easy access to your belongings, while the lockable zip will keep your posessions safe when it's out of sight. Fully padded shoulder straps make this bag extremely comfortable to carry.

Name: Ladies Nautic Sandal
Description: Musto’s Nautic Sandal is designed for warm days when you want to feel the air on your feet but still need to wear dependable, non-slip footwear. The rubber outsole has faux siping for increased traction and the strap is made from padded, breathable air-mesh for additional comfort.

Name: Women's Active Base Layer Long Sleeve Top
Description: Designed for high energy activities, this Women's Active Base Layer has been constructed using minimal seams to reduce chaffing when active and maximise comfort beneath outer layers. Exceptionally fast-wicking with strategically placed variable knits, this top combines muscle support and heat retention to help the body recover from exercise faster and prevent injury. An anti-bacterial Nilit® Bodyfresh treatment prevents odour when wearing the top over extended periods.

Name: Women's Evolution Sunblock Short Sleeve T-shirt 2.0

Name: LPX GORE-TEX® Short
Description: When on a wet boat in warm conditions, reach for your LPX GORE-TEX Shorts. Reinforced in the high-wear seat area with 600 denier abrasion-resistant fabric, this garment will be an enduring kit bag essential. A high back with a lightly padded waistband provides coverage as you move, while a double belt loop makes for easy attachment of tools.

Name: Foiling Sunblock Impact Top
Description: Constructed from lightweight, fast-drying, UPF50-treated fabric, the Foiling Sunblock Impact Top is designed to protect when sailing high-speed foiling boats. Internal pockets can accommodate cutting-edge D3O® impact protection pads on areas most at risk of injury on the shoulders, elbows and forearms. These highly flexible D3O® pads work by moving with your body and hardening on impact, absorbing the shock through molecules that lock together. Wear alone or layered under your wetsuit or smock.

Name: Sardinia Rain Jacket
Description: Windproof and waterproof, the Sardinia Rain Jacket has fully taped seams and a 2-layer fabric construction that will protect you in even the worst of storms. It's also mesh lined for total comfort and breathability and features a fixed hood, adjustable cuffs and YKK® zips for additional protection against the elements.

Name: Whisper Highland GORE-TEX® Primaloft® Jacket
Description: The Whisper GORE-TEX® PrimaLoft® Jacket features supremely smooth brushed fabric with a tricot face. A GORE Woodland Liner provides windproof, waterproof and breathable protection while a Durable Water Repellent coating adds further weather-resistance. PrimaLoft® Silver insulation delivers incredible warmth while the waist adjuster can be used via the handwarmer pockets.

Name: EVOLUTION PRIMALOFT PARKA
Description: Whether you’re heading into the wilderness or just outside in poor weather, the Evolution PrimaLoft® Parka will keep you protected from the elements. The outer layer is waterproof to our BR1 standard and the jacket features PrimaLoft® Black Insulation which offers exceptionally lightweight warmth and softness. Practical but stylish - warm but cool.

Name: Evolution Sailing Belt
Description: Designed with Musto branded tape, this Evolution Sailing Belt features a heavy-duty polyester canvas webbed construction. Fastened with a D-ring for a secure closure.

Name: Flexlite Alumin Long John 2.5mm
Description: Made to deliver exceptional protection and truly superior freedom of movement. This Flexlite Alumin Long John 2.5mm are constructed from neoprene that is 15-20% lighter and stretchier than the standard range, this garment delivers a remarkably unrestricted spectrum of motion. Unique to Musto, this garment features a 4-layer construction, with an alumin thermal rebound for prolonged increased heat retention in colder waters. A firm favourite amongst Olympic sailors.

Name: EVOLUTION NEWPORT OSM PRIMALOFT® ACTIVE JACKET
Description: The Evolution Newport OSM PrimaLoft® Active Jacket is both sustainable and stylish. It’s made from one single material which makes it much easier to recycle at the end of its life and its colour is achieved with solution dye which uses 85% less water and 90% less harmful chemicals. PrimaLoft® Silver Eco Insulation, made from 100% recycled polyester, provides exceptional eco-friendly warmth without adding bulk.

Name: Foiling Deck Shield Hikers
Description: Constructed from durable, lightweight and streamlined super-stretch 1.5mm neoprene (2.5mm including the neoprene backer and face thickness). These Foiling Deck Shield Hikers provide protection exactly where you need it, with strategic reinforcements made from advanced abrasion-resistant nylon. For outstanding support and protection, anatomical baton pads can be positioned as required.

Name: Foiling ThermoCOOL Long Sleeve Top
Description: Made from 1.5mm (2.5mm thickness including the neoprene backer and face thickness) from super-stretch neoprene, this incredibly engineered garment features a scooped hem that covers your lower back as you bend. Strategically placed seams ensure an ergonomic fit while avoiding stress points for a greater degree of durability and enhanced freedom of movement. Layer under a sleeveless wetsuit or complete your outfit with Deck Shield Pants.

Name: EVOLUTION PACKABLE RAIN JACKET
Description: This jacket provides heavy duty rain protection in lightweight packable form. Above industry standard 5K/5K waterproof fabric and fully taped seams ensure you remain protected in even the most persistent downpours, while Musto's unique GRIPHOOD provides additional protection, stays put in high winds and doesn't compromise your peripheral vision when you turn your head.

Name: Foiling Race Bib
Description: Constructed from anatomical stretch fabric, pull on this Foiling Race Bib over your buoyancy aid when racing. A superior streamlined fit and UPF40 protection safeguards you from the sun. Elasticated armholes and silicon gripper inside the hem ensures a comfort fit that won't ride up for unrestricted racing. Branding is available for this garment.

Name: Breathable Sou'wester
Description: An enduring Musto collection staple, this Breathable Sou'wester features a fully seam taped construction that is as waterproof as it is breathable. A durable water repellent (DWR) treatment ensures enhanced protection against rain and spray. An ergonomically shaped brim scooped around the neck protects you against the sun while a drawstring adjustment under your chin helps secure the hat during windy weather. Consider this essential protection for any day sailor.

Name: KNITTED BEANIE
Description: Constructed from 100% microfleece, the Musto Knitted Beanie is stylish, snug, and ideal for when the weather gets chilly.

Name: Qingdao Sunblock Short Sleeve Polo
Description: Stay protected. Stay active. The Sunblock Short Sleeve Polo features a remarkable UPF 40 fabric construction. Flatlocked seams are barely detectable against your skin for comfort when active.

Name: Championship Deck Shield Short
Description: The Championship Deck Shield Short ensures superior protection so you can stay on the water for longer. A 3mm neoprene construction features lightweight and resilient padding in the seat and back of the thighs. 1.5mm abrasion-resistant nylon provides impressive resilience that withstands the rigours of active sailing. Breathable, stretch fabric with an advanced UPF50 treatment safeguards your skin from the sun and provides unrestricted movement.

Name: Sunblock Dynamic Long John
Description: Featuring an Ultraviolet Protection Factor (UPF) of 50, the Sunblock Dynamic Long John will keep you protected from strong sun exposure. The fabrication is infused with Xylitol, an active cooling agent that will help you stay comfortable in even the most humid conditions, and the garment also features Kevlar® which prevents wear and protects the fabric from abrasion on the seat and knees.

Name: Frome Mid Layer Trouser
Description: These Frome Mid Layer Trousers: a new addition to the collection. These have been constructed from advanced, fleece-lined fabric. Anatomical articulation offers full freedom of movement. Ideal for those that prefer a waist fitted trouser under their waterproof outer-layer. Supremely breathable, highly durable and unrestrictive.

Name: EVOLUTION NEWPORT OSM PRIMALOFT® PARKA
Description: Designed in collaboration with 11th Hour Racing, our Evolution Newport OSM PRIMALOFT® Parka delivers style and substance for conscientious adventurers who care about protecting the environment as much as they do themselves. The jacket is constructed from One Single Material (OSM) which makes it much easier to recycle at the end of its life. This is especially important for the environment as recycling fibres helps to reduce the overuse of raw virgin materials. Complete with Musto’s BR2 performance technology and PRIMALOFT® Silver Eco insulation – 100% recycled polyester - this jacket still delivers on our commitment to utilising premium fabric technologies without compromising on sustainability or style.

Name: Foiling ThermoHOT Impact Steamer
Description: This Foiling Impact Steamer is engineered for foiling race performance in the cold. Super-stretch 4mm (5mm including the backer and face) neoprene and ergonomic seams give you exceptional freedom of movement and insulation in cold conditions. Anti-abrasion nylon on the knees, seat and legs protects you from the deck. Internal pockets allow cutting-edge D3O® impact protection pads to be placed on the back, shoulders, elbows, forearms, hips, outer thighs and shins (pads not included).

Name: MEN'S SAILGP FRA T-SHIRT
Description: A classic summer tee. The SailGP FRA T-Shirt has been constructed from soft cotton jersey. Musto red yacht branding is embroidered on the back yoke to provide a subtle, nautical detail. Choose from a variety of colours.

Name: Neoprene Kneepads
Description: Moving boats can take their toll on your knees. Minimise the impact of knocks and benefit from cushioned knee protection in these exceptional Neoprene Kneepads. Anatomically constructed to safeguard you so you can focus on your performance. Suitable for all types of sailing.

Name: British Sailing Team Short Sleeve T-shirt
Description: This is your classic summer Crew T-Shirt in a soft cotton jersey. There are a variety of colours to choose from too. A small, Musto red yacht is embroidered at the bottom left hem and in the centre back of the neck providing subtle, nautical details.

Name: Aiden Short Sleeve Oxford Shirt
Description: Made from breathable 100% Oxford cotton, the Aiden Oxford Short Sleeve Shirt features single edge stitching for a polished finish. A self-fabric chest pocket to the front features Musto’s Red Boat embroidery for a smart finish.

Name: Fleece Lined Waterproof Cap
Description: Critically seam taped with a fleece lining for incredible heat retention, this Fleece-Lined Cap ensures superior weather protection. The peaked front helps shield your eyes in bright sunlight. Fold-down flaps cover your ears and neck, helping you stay warm when the weather turns. Keep the hat in place by using the drawstring adjustment during windy weather.

Name: Championship Hydrothermal Top
Description: The Championship Hydrothermal Top offers superior water-repellent warmth. This incredibly versatile garment can be worn as a base layer underneath a wetsuit, drysuit or smock for enhanced heat retention. A stretch fabric construction and the elimination of seams ensure superior movement and ergonomic comfort.

Name: Unicef Sunblock Short Sleeve Polo
Description: Stay protected. Stay active. The Sunblock Short Sleeve Polo features a remarkable UPF 40 fabric construction. Flatlocked seams are barely detectable against your skin for comfort when active.

Name: Musto 90L Duffel Bag
Description: Whether you're off on a long voyage or embarking on a big adventure, the Musto 90L Duffel Bag is lightweight, durable and provides you with easy access to your belongings, while the lockable zip will keep your posessions safe when it's out of sight. Fully padded shoulder straps make this bag extremely comfortable to carry.

Name: Youth Championship ThermoHOT Top
Description: This Youth Championship ThermoHOT Neoprene Top features a loop an advanced thermospan backer for exceptional warmth. Super-stretch 4mm neoprene (5mm insulation when including the neoprene backer and face thickness) combines complete freedom of movement with an superior heat retention. Ergonomic, flatlocked seams have been strategically placed to avoid all stress points so you can enjoy incredible comfort when active.

Name: Youth Insignia UV Fast Dry Short Sleeve T-Shirt
Description: The Youth Insignia UV Fast Dry Rash Guard has been constructed from a technical, moisture-wicking fabric for enhanced comfort. Antibacterial properties ensure prolonged hygiene and odour-control with UPF 40 for protection from the sun. High-grade flatlock seams lie flat against your skin for greater comfort as a base layer.

Name: Frome Mid Layer Salopette
Description: Fleece lined for superior warmth and insulation, these Frome Mid Layer Salopettes offer impeccable insulation out on the water. Elastication along the back of the waist delivers prolonged comfort and freedom of movement on the boat. Featuring an updated aesthetic with signature Musto red trims. Designed for freezing conditions when adding a layer of warmth is paramount. Worn by Volvo Ocean Race sailors as part of Musto's 3-layer system.

Name: EVOLUTION PRIMALOFT HYBRID TROUSERS
Description: With stretch fabric below the knee and PrimaLoft® Black insulated fabric on the thigh, these trousers are the perfect balance of flexibility, durability and comfort. Secure zip pockets will keep your belongings safe while you’re on the move.

Name: Insignia UV Fast Dry Short Sleeve T-Shirt
Description: A stretch fabric construction to ensure superior freedom of movement. The absence of underarm seams eradicates chaffing when active. This Insignia UV Fast Dry Short Sleeve T-Shirt is the ideal garment for active wear. Constructed with UPF 40 protection to safeguard you from the sun's harmful UV rays.

Name: Championship Hydrothermal Pant
Description: These ChampionshipThermoFLEX Pants have been made from hydrophobic fleece for versatile and advanced water-repellent warmth. Reinforced nylon has been strategically placed to enhance the durability of the garment. Stretch fabric with ergonomic, flatlocked seams ensure greater comfort when active.

Name: Merino Long Sleeve T-Shirt
Description: Constructed from merino wool: the ultimate natural fabric for active wear. Supremely moisture- and temperature-regulating, this fabric enhances comfort by being naturally anti-bacterial and remarkably soft. Wool fibres wick moisture away from the body to keep you dry and outstandingly comfortable while trapping vital warmth in cold climates.

Name: MUSTO X LAND ROVER GTX PARKA
Description: Extreme protection for high-octane adventures. The Land Rover GORE-TEX Parka is packed with cutting edge tech that will keep you warm, dry and protected in even the most volatile conditions.

Name: Corsica Polo
Description: Constructed from quick dry Tactel® double pique, the Corsica Polo is ideal for high energy activity out at sea. A button front placket and ribbed collar and cuffs with contrast stripes makes this shirt both sensible and striking.

Name: HTX GORE-TEX LITE JACKET
Description: When you’re out hunting, you never know where the day will take you. That’s why you need a lightweight jacket that provides heavy-duty protection against changeable environments and weather conditions. 2-layer GORE-TEX will keep you dry without adding bulk and multiple pockets and features will ensure you can adapt to any situation you find yourself in.

Name: SHAKER CUFF BEANIE
Description: Versatile, warm and extremely comfortable, you can't go wrong with the Shaker Cuff Beanie. The 12GG double knit is designed to trap warm air and keeps out the elements.

Name: Sunblock Dynamic Short Sleeve T-Shirt
Description: If you're planning to undertake intense activity in hot conditions, the Sunblock Dynamic Short Sleeve T-Shirt is the garment for you. Featuring an Ultraviolet Protection Factor (UPF) of 50, the tee will protect you from strong sun exposure. It also features a scooped hem for a comfortable fit, flatlocked seams that won't chafe against your skin and there are no underarm seams to ensure you remain comfortable and your arm movements are not restricted.

Name: EVOLUTION SOFTSHELL SMOCK
Description: Constructed from waterproof, softshell material, the evolution smock is the ideal lightweight solution for hardcore outdoor activities. Musto’s unique and innovative GRIPHOOD stays put in strong winds and rotates with your head, keeping it protected without compromising your peripheral vision.

Name: BR1 Short
Description: Made to Musto's exemplary BR1 standard. These BR1 Shorts feature a reinforced seat panel for enhanced durability when working on a boat in fair weather. A tricot brushed lining provides impressive comfort next-to-skin while elastication in the waist provides a tailored fit. Stay exceptionally dry on wet decks thanks to taped seams throughout. Available in two colours to complement your choice of jacket.

Name: EVOLUTION BOARD SHORT
Description: The Evo Board Shorts balance relaxed style with a high- performance edge.

Name: GORE-TEX® Middle Layer Salopette
Description: A favourite of Volvo Ocean Race sailors. A supremely warm, technical Arctec fleece lining in this GORE-TEX® Mid-Layer Salopette allows you to face freezing temperatures in complete comfort. Stretch shoulders and articulated seat and knees provide complete freedom of movement with abrasion-resistant, strategic reinforcements for durability. Layer it up - tapered legs ensure enhanced comfort under outer layers. The ultimate mid-layer salopette for long-distance sailing.

Name: British Sailing Team Race Visor
Description: Show your support for an incredible team while enjoying enhanced protection on the boat. Constructed from fast-drying fabric, this British Sailing Team Race Visor ensures comfort and enhanced visibility on the boat.

Name: CORSICA PRIMALOFT FUNNEL JACKET
Description: Wind resistant, water repellent and lined with premium PrimaLoft® Silver Insulation, the Corsica PrimaLoft® Funnel Jacket provides comfortable and durable protection from the elements. Contrast piping at the collar and the printed Musto logo at the back provide smart, subtle details that make this jacket stand out.

Name: Championship Deck Shield Pant
Description: Made from super-stretch, breathable and resilient 3mm neoprene, these UPF-treated Championship Deck Shield Pants feature 1.5mm abrasion-resistant nylon for enhanced durability. Padding in the seat and back of the thighs provide impeccable comfort combined with advanced moulded rubber DeckShield knee protection.

Name: EVOLUTION PRIMALOFT SHELL JACKET
Description: With sustainable PrimaLoft® Black Eco insulation on the inside and a 2-layer stretch fabric that's waterproof to our BR1 standard on the outside, the Evolution PrimaLoft® Jacket provides hardcore protection in even the most volatile conditions.

Name: Montrose BR1 Jacket
Description: Featuring Musto's unique BR1, two-layer fabric and polysuede shoulder panels, this jacket is sophisticated in both its aesthetic and its power to protect you from the elements. The taffeta lining provides impeccable comfort while the adjustable waist enables enhanced warmth and a flattering fit.

Name: Youth Championship ThermoHOT Wetsuit
Description: Highly versatile, dynamically stretchy and incredibly insulating. This Youth Championship ThermoHOT Wetsuit has been constructed from durable super stretch 4mm neoprene (5mm including the neoprene backer and face). Resilient Deck Shield knees and abrasion-resistant nylon in high wear areas ensure a robust construction that withstands the demands of dinghy sailing. High-grade, anatomical flat-stitching and the elimination of seams altogether in places ensure truly superior comfort on the water.

Name: Evolution Performance Short 2.0
Description: These are hard-wearing performance sailing shorts. The lightweight, fast dry stretch fabric gives full freedom of movement and comfort. Schoeller®-keprotec® reinforcement on the seat provides hard-wearing durability. Back and thigh pockets keep your possessions close and secure.

Name: ESS 3 PACK TRAINER SOCK
Description: Lightweight and breathable with exceptional stretch, these socks are essential for a reason.

Name: Thermal Base Layer Long Sleeve Top
Description: This Thermal Base Layer Long Sleeve Top has been constructed from quick dry, fast-wicking fabric for exceptional comfort when active. Flatlock seams minimise chaffing during period of exertion. An antibacterial finish ensures fresher wear on long offshore passages. Featuring an improved fit and construction for the new season.

Name: Waterproof Dry Backpack 40L
Description: Keep your belongings protected, even in torrential rain and heavy spray in this Waterproof Dry 40L Backpack. Constructed using an innovative bonded construction that eliminates the need for stitching and zips, this accessory provides stormproof protection for your essentials. Secured by a hardwearing buckle this large bag features durable carry handles and padded shoulder straps.

Name: Evolution Race Visor
Description: Benefit from the comfort and visibility on the boat in this Evolution Race Visor. Constructed from fast-drying fabric.

Name: Pique Polo
Description: A clean, timeless polo in an array of bold statement colours, providing something for everyday wear. Garment washed and ribbed collar and cuff for comfort next to skin in a relaxed, comfortable fit. The perfect wardrobe staple this season.

Name: BR1 Inshore Jacket
Description: The BR1 Inshore Jacket, with its taped seams and exceptional BR1 Musto fabric construction, supplies a superior level of waterproof and windproof protection. Double cuffs a storm flap zip guard and drawcord hem seal water out for exceptional dryness. The technical rollaway, fluorescent hood adds visibility as well as enhancing the garment’s waterproof protection. The two fleece-lined pockets and collar keep your hands and neck warm in cool coastal winds.

Name: Essential Fast Dry Crew Cap
Description: The Essential Fast Dry Crew Cap: a fast-drying, UV-protective accessory for enhanced comfort in the sun and when active. The peak shields your eyes from the sun, and the rear adjustment gives you a secure fit. Attach the retainer clip to reduce the risk of losing it in high winds.

Name: GORE-TEX® Middle Layer Blouson
Description: This waterproof and breathable Mid Layer GORE-TEX® Blouson is lined in exceptionally warm Arctec 240 grid fleece to ensure that it is the ultimate middle layer for long distance sailing. The close-fitting collar sits comfortably beneath another jacket with full articulation for free movement. Technical fluorescent trims keep you visible when wearing this as an outer layer in low light.

Name: Championship Smock
Description: When you're racing, you need kit that goes the distance. This Championship Smock features a super-durable, waterproof and breathable 3-layer fabric construction, with 4-way stretch fabric and ergonomic seaming for superior freedom of movement. An elasticated hem and advanced silicon gripper offers a comfort fit that moves with you. Engineered reflective detailing keeps you highly visible in low light conditions.

Name: HPX GORE-TEX Ocean Jacket
Description: The HPX Ocean Jacket: impeccably waterproof, exceptionally windproof and remarkably breathable. Constructed from a softer 3-layer GORE-TEX Pro fabric with an Ocean Technology® membrane and a GORE Micro Grid Backer for total durability and warmth in the harshest conditions. Stretch panels across the upper back and arms ensure freedom of movement. Incredibly abrasion-resistant CORDURA® seat patches have been strategically placed in high-wear areas to enhance resilience. A fluorescent hood and advanced photoluminescent reflectors light up to pinpoint your location in dark conditions. Large handwarmer pockets and an engineered fleece lining on the high collar keep you warm in freezing conditions.

Name: BR2 Coastal Jacket
Description: Outstandingly waterproof, highly breathable and remarkably durable. The BR2 Coastal Jacket has been constructed from high performance, proprietary BR2 fabric that keeps you dry and comfortable, whilst an articulated cut ensures a full spectrum of motion ideal for the active sailor. For enhanced protection, the garment features a technical double storm flap, fluorescent hood and fleece lined handwarmer pockets. Advanced reflective detailing keep you visible in low light.

Name: Extreme Thermal Fleece Top
Description: This Extreme Thermal Fleece Top delivers incredible warmth. A highly engineered fleece backer enhances heat retention with a turtle neck design that traps body heat with increased efficiency. Flatlocked seams boosts durability whilst providing greater comfort when active. Treated with durable water repellent (DWR), water beads off the fleece, adding protection against the elements.

Name: MPX GORE-TEX Pro Offshore Smock
Description: The MPX Offshore Smock - impeccably engineered for the active offshore sailor. Constructed from 3-layer GORE-TEX Pro, this smock offers outstanding waterproof protection that's also incredibly breathable to keep you comfortable in the worst weather. A darted sleeve construction ensures exceptional articulation for complete freedom of movement. Musto's pioneering HPX Jacket inspired the hood construction on this garment, which is why it features an exceptional heat retentive grid fleece lined funnel and hood pod and a highly innovative and protective adjustable spume. This sets the benchmark for the new generation in offshore protection.

Name: Clay Shooting Vest
Description: Designed to give you the inside edge when clay shooting. This Clay Shooting Vest features durable Clarino reinforcement panels for durability that aids gun mount stability. Time to reload: large cartridge pockets allow you to reach your cartridges quickly. And rubber rivets reduce the risk of gunstock damage while providing easy access to equipment. A pocket for a D3O® recoil pad protects you against recoil impact from your gun.

Name: GORE-TEX Ocean Racer
Description: The GORE-TEX Ocean Racer Boot: made for the harshest conditions. For complete waterproof protection and optimal breathability, the boot features the toughest GORE-TEX footwear membrane available. The CORDURA® upper and gaiter ensures outstanding durability. Areas prone to abrasion damage have also been reinforced with scratch rubber for complete protection. GripDeck rubber and a GripFlex tread to supplies exceptional, multi-directional traction on deck. And a unique DynamicFit bellowed tongue and bungee lacing system provides a locked-down, comfort fit.

Name: Genoa Mini Carryall
Description: Engineered from splash-resistant fabric, this classic Genoa Mini Carryall features a heavy-duty zip closure. A velcro side pocket supplies secure storage while a removable, adjustable shoulder strap ensures easy transportation.

Name: MPX GORE-TEX Pro Race Smock
Description: Made from exceptional 3-layer GORE-TEX PRO in an articulated design, this MPX Pro Race Smock combines complete freedom of movement with the superior protection you need to focus on the race. Its durable design safeguards you in the most extreme weather conditions. A 3mm neoprene waistband with shell fabric side panels offers a watertight seal and heat retention as well as a remarkable degree of flex.

Name: MARINA BEANIE
Description: With a traditional fisherman fit, the stylish and sustainable Marina Beanie is made from one single material meaning the garment will be much easier to recycle at the end of its life. A 100% polyester fleece lining provides exceptional warmth and the hat is quick drying, ensuring your head stays warm and protected when exposed to the elements.

Name: Active Base Layer Zip Neck Top
Description: Minimal seams for maximum comfort. This fast-wicking top provides exceptional comfort during high energy activities. Strategically placed variable knits offer muscle support to prevent injury and increase heat retention to help the body recover from activity. Anti-bacterial Nilit® Bodyfresh treatment prevents odour when wearing the top over extended periods.

Name: MPX GORE-TEX Pro Race Jacket
Description: Race unrestricted and fully protected in this MPX Pro Race Jacket. Advanced GORE-TEX PRO, 3-layer waterproof fabric safeguards you in the most extreme weather conditions while remaining completely breathable. A foldaway, drawcord-adjusted hood with a brushed tricot lining enhances the garment's exceptional waterproof design and versatility in race conditions. A superior range of motion is offered through the garment's anatomically constructed articulated sleeves.

Name: MARINA QUILTED JACKET 2.0
Description: With a subtle matte finish, the Marina Quilted Jacket 2.0 is a reworked and updated version of the classic original Marina Quilted Jacket, and the perfect balance of protection and style. Lined with dynamic insulation, it maintains warmth even when wet and provides the luxurious feel of down in a synthetic performance jacket.

Name: Active Base Layer Trousers
Description: Minimal seams for maximum comfort. These fast-wicking trousers provide exceptional comfort during high energy activities. Strategically placed variable knits offer muscle support to prevent injury and increase heat retention to help the body recover from activity. Anti-bacterial Nilit® Bodyfresh treatment prevents odour when wearing the garment over extended periods

Name: MARINA LONG-SLEEVE T-SHIRT
Description: Stylish long sleeve tee made from 100% organic cotton with a chest print and flag branding.

Name: MPX GORE-TEX Pro Offshore Jacket
Description: The Musto MPX Collection features an updated fit for the new season. This MPX Offshore Jacket's improved cut ensures an exceptional level of comfort with a darted sleeve construction for enhanced articulation. A 3-layer GORE-TEX Pro fabric construction supplies outstanding waterproof protection that's also incredibly breathable to keep you comfortable in all weather. Inspired by the hood construction on the brand's pioneering HPX Jacket, the MPX Offshore Jacket features a heat retentive grid fleece lined funnel and hood pod with a highly protective, adjustable spume. Experience the new generation in offshore protection.

Name: CORSICA PRIMALOFT® RAIN JACKET
Description: Whether you’re at the coast, on the moors or in the city – it’s going to rain. The Corsica PrimaLoft® Rain Jacket delivers the distinctive yet transitional style that makes it the ideal garment to protect you in any environment. A ‘winterised’ version of our successful Corsica 2.0 range with a longer length and understated silhouette - both on-trend for this season.

Name: ESSENTIAL FULL ZIP SWEAT
Description: Constructed from 100% polyester loopback, the Essential Full Zip Sweat is comfortable, absorbent and the ideal active garment. A reverse coil zip front, tonal embroidered funnel neck and bound cuff give it a sporty, luxe finish.

Name: LPX SUNBLOCK DYNAMIC LS TEE
Description: Beat the heat and the competition with the LPX Sunblock Dynamic Long Sleeve Tee. Constructed from innovative ICE CAFÉ yarn that provides the active cooling effect of Xylitol - capable of lowering body temperature by up to 3 degrees without additional chemicals - and incorporates liquified post-consumer waste coffee beans that combat odour and maintain freshness; this tee is guaranteed to keep you cool and confident in periods of intense exertion in warmer climates. The material also reflects harmful UV rays and has SPF50 for additional sun protection, while the flatlock shifted shoulder seams and articulated panelling ensure total comfort and freedom of movement.

Name: Evolution Sunblock Short Sleeve T-shirt 2.0
Description: Block harmful UV rays while you train, work out or explore in this fast-drying Evolution Sunblock T-Shirt. Its UPF 50 treated, wicking cotton-polyester blend means you'll always stay dry and comfortable.

Name: EVOLUTION FULL ZIP TECH SWEAT
Description: A full zip contemporary twist on a traditional fleece, constructed with spacer fabric for extra comfort and stretch.

Name: MUSTO X LAND ROVER PRIMALOFT VEST
Description: With featherlight PrimaLoft® Black Eco insulation, this vest will keep you agile, warm and protected during intense activity, or when you're out in the wilderness and braving the elements.

Name: Evolution Yacht Belt
Description: The smart and durable Evolution Yacht Belt. Made for the modern sailor, on and off the boat. The corrosion-resistant clip and stopper are built to withstand life at sea. Finished in matte black for a sleek aesthetic, with a subtle, embossed Musto yacht. A hidden bottle opener in the back of the buckle is ideal for drinks on deck.

Name: MUSTO X LAND ROVER POCKET TEE
Description: Constructed from 100% cotton with Land Rover inspired detailing to the chest pocket.

Name: LPX GORE-TEX® Jacket
Description: Inspired by Musto�s original LPX Jacket, this lightweight and breathable LPX GORE-TEX Jacket is ideal for high-performance inshore or coastal sailing in warmer conditions. Layer up for cold weather protection. Made from durable polyester 3-layer GORE-TEX, this jacket ensures resilient protection for many seasons to come. A brushed tricot collar provides heat retention and comfort next-to-skin, while a pared-back design and articulated elbows deliver complete freedom of movement.
